Package cz.cuni.mff.bluebench.operations

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateIndexes
    Operation which creates indexes in the graph.
    Dijkstra
    Performs Dijkstra's algorithm on the graph.
    FindEdgesByProperty
    Operation which searches the graph for edges with a specified property.
    FindNeighbours
    Operation which gets the neighbors of a specified vertex.
    FindVerticesByProperty
    Operation which searches the graph for vertices with a specified property.
    LoadGraphML
    Loads the graph database with a provided GraphML file.
    RemoveVertices
    Removes a number of vertices from the graph.
    ShortestPath
    Performs a shortest path search between two specified vertices.
    ShortestPathLabeled
    Performs a labeled shortest path search between two specified vertices.
    Traversal
    Performs a BFS traversal from a provided vertex.
    TraversalNative
    Performs a BFS traversal from a provided vertex (native versions of the algorithms).
    UpdateEdgeProperties
    Updates properties of specified edges.
    UpdateProperties
    Updates properties of specified vertices.
